{"tid":2486307,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–癌症所導致的體重流失(2)","createTime":"2021-04-12T21:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T08:18:37.000Z","uid":38861,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"52309e6af8c456f32adae509835b48a8cea3b6c7","tid":2486307,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T21:59:10.000Z","msg":"此為上集的補充篇:三十秒科學&ndash;癌症所導致的體重流失<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2397914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2397914</a><br />\n<br />\n癌症惡病質(cancer cachexia)泛指因癌症而導致的體重流失，大部份情況下主要是由喪失肌肉所致，並沒法依靠進食來填補其喪失。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRa4hspjSZmCpGG95GhMufQP4fCGpcwZf3MgX2epsXopx?filename=z1ExxfA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1ExxfA.png&h=09656dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在眾多癌症之中，高達接近70%的胰臟癌病人會出現cancer cachexia，總體重的損失在六個月內可高達25%。<br />\n相反，患上前列腺癌的病人僅只有約10%的人出現cancer cachexia。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)病人出現cancer cachexia的話(以體重損失超過10%為指標)，其生存的機率亦會因而顯著下降。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR6kGpb8VojHz7dST2k4ktfxRzXcGiqWC51e9JWmvE3pN?filename=ViKd083.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FViKd083.png&h=2928ae73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正因如此，若能了解其cancer cachexia機制並加以針對的話，將會是抵抗癌症的其中一道手法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)癌細胞所導致的體重流失，主要是由肌肉喪失所致。<br />\n而當我們的肌肉受到傷害或撕裂的時候，裡頭的幹細胞以及圖中所指的細胞將會出手幫忙製造肌肉，填補其損失。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQeQjaifrEsthfea7k1fAae3FeMMoQ5mXk9wNAiRjKPSF?filename=ot8BYVO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fot8BYVO.png&h=a0d234e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n癌細胞的厲害之處就是能夠釋出物質經由血管到達肌肉，誘導肌肉出現受傷情況之餘，並同時阻止肌肉幹細胞進行重生，因而導致肌肉流失情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n癌細胞之所以這樣做，其中的一道推論是希望透過破壞肌肉而使血液間的氨基酸(蛋白質)含量增加，然後借助肝臟把這些氨基酸轉變成糖份，再由血液循環系統輸送給自身所用。<br />\n<br />\n因著胰臟癌病人出現cancer cachexia的機率較高，有不少科學家均就此利用老鼠胰臟癌模型來研究cancer cachexia的機制。<br />\n<br />\n至今已至少找出得到，癌細胞所釋出的物質會導致肌肉幹細胞一種名為Pax7的蛋白質含量不斷上升，並因而導致肌肉幹細胞沒法子進行重組肌肉舉動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DME4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=b6c78d4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DME4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=f2c3cc37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/nrdp2017105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fnrdp2017105&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DME4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=a2c4b129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/nrdp2017105</a>"},{"pid":"ed37636afe1029d9ff74add4c2c4c3a5163ac7a2","tid":2486307,"uid":75487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T22:02:25.000Z","msg":"Ho info gchi"},{"pid":"10bb46d0bd58a099e820a49a555c65f4eeeac3b5","tid":2486307,"uid":62328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T22:08:05.000Z",