gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb92cdcc6e5630511761963303ead953f8d3da6","tid":2486307,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"老母就係胰臟CAN 走既..最仆街係勁難發現..一黎就第四期"},{"pid":"5984035384bcd6a4b9cbecd8bfc77a96428c3faf","tid":2486307,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0ecd1e3805937a0a3c58ff74fa0af19deb8cd9f7","tid":2486307,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"直接打自由基落癌細胞落去有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda6dda3d1e0ccd58fde8246f27ffd19e5f395a1","tid":2486307,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"相關資訊分享返<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 甚麼徵狀顯示患上胰臟癌？<br />\n如果大家有以下徵狀，可能是患上胰臟癌：<br />\n- 上腹部出現與飲食無關的持續疼痛, 並會反射至背部<br />\n- 食慾不振、噁心、嘔吐、消化不良、腹脹等腸胃障礙現象<br />\n- 出現黃疸、皮膚搔癢、大便呈陶土色<br />\n- 體重短時間內銳減<br />\n- 上腹部出現固定、堅硬的腫塊<br />\n- 腹水<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">醫管局 - 智友站 - 胰臟癌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www21.ha.org.hk/smartpatient/SPW/zh-hk/Disease-Information/Disease/?guid=074209a8-91f7-4223-8b41-d46d43b4e28c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww21.ha.org.hk%2Fsmartpatient%2FSPW%2Fzh-hk%2FDisease-Information%2FDisease%2F%3Fguid%3D074209a8-91f7-4223-8b41-d46d43b4e28c&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DME4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=a13aab91\" target=\"_blank\">https://www21.ha.org.hk/smartpatient/SPW/zh-hk/Disease-Information/Disease/?guid=074209a8-91f7-4223-8b41-d46d43b4e28c</a></span>"},{"pid":"d13f3aef8f758290cf647e6480688224c383cd1b","tid":2486307,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6185ea9d52606be8f8313c24a5d313401f3055fa","tid":2486307,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:40:38